high_descs: go forward to the counter top
pick up the yellow handle knife from the counter top
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the left and and go past the counter and turn to the right and take a few steps and turn left and go to the counter top
with the knife slice up the loaf of bread on the counter top
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the right and take a step and turn to the left and go to the wall and turn to the left and go to the microwave
open the microwave door and put the knife in it and close the microwave door
turn to the left twice and take a step and turn to the right and go to the front of the loaf of bread on the counter and turn to the right and go to the counter top
take a slice of bread from the counter top
turn to the left twice and take a step and turn to the right and go to the front of the refrigerator and turn to the right and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator top door and put the bread slice in the top compartment and close the door and wait and open the door and take out bread slice and close the refrigerator door.
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the right and take a step and turn to the left and go to the wall and turn to the left and go to the microwave
open the microwave door and put the bread slice  in it and close the microwave door

high_descs: Walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to face the bread on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Step to the right to face the microwave on the counter.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Step to the left to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn right and cross the room and turn left to face the microwave.
Place the bread slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bread slice and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the side of the sink.
Turn around to the counter right of the fridge.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Go to the fridge.
Cool off the bread in the fridge.
Take the cold bread to the microwave.
Put the cold bread into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold piece of bread in the microwave.
